ateeminen Kirjakauppa]] (\"The Academic Bookstore\")<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.akateeminen.com/ |title=Akateeminen Kirjakauppa |website=Akateeminen.com |date= |accessdate=2016-09-25}}</ref>\n*[[Suomalainen Kirjakauppa]] (\"The Finnish Bookstore\")<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.suomalainen.com/ |title=nettikirjakauppa |language=fi |website=Suomalainen.com |date= |accessdate=2016-09-25}}</ref>\n\n==[[France]]==\n<!-- DO NOT add names of bookstore chains to this list unless they already have Wikipedia articles, or could reasonably be expected to be the subject of an article or article section based on their notability NOW. For businesses not linked to their own articles, you MUST add at least one reference from a reliable source indicating their notability as a chain bookstore, or the business WILL be removed. This is not a directory of businesses! -->\n* [[Groupe Flammarion|Flammarion]]\n* [[Fnac]] (78 stores with book departments in [[France]], 65 in 8 other countries)\n* [[Hachette Distribution Services]]\n\n==[[Germany]]==\n<!-- DO NOT add names of bookstore chains to this list unless they already have Wikipedia articles, or could reasonably be expected to be the subject of an article or article section based on their notability NOW. For businesses not linked to their own articles, you MUST add at least one reference from a reliable source indicating their notability as a chain bookstore, or the business WILL be removed. This is not a directory of businesses! -->\n*[[Hugendubel]] (34 book-department-stores)\n*[[Thalia (bookstore)|Thalia]]\n*[[Verlagsgruppe Weltbild]], Weltbild Plus, Weltbild, Weltbild best, Jokers, Wohlthat (circa 350-400 shops)\n\n==[[Greece]]==\n* [[Eleutheroudakis]]\n* [[Ianos]]\n* [[Papasotiriou]]\n* [[Pothitos]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pothitosbooks.gr |title=PothitosBooks - \u0392\u03b9\u03b2\u03bb\u03b9\u03bf\u03c0\u03c9\u03bb\u03b5\u03af\u03bf - \u0392\u03b9\u03b2\u03bb\u03af\u03b1 \u03c3\u03b5 \u03a0\u03c1\u03bf\u03c3\u03c6\u03bf